  "body": "### Help to reproduce is needed\r\nIf you can reproduce it, please, make a comment with \r\n* Steps to reproduce (if available). \r\n* Any special conditions/data/settings (e.g. slow connection, first run, run app after it was not used for several days, any other special info)\r\n* Have you tried same steps or check data later? Have you waited for any feedback from the app and for how long?\r\n* Any extra comments you have\r\n* Status version\r\n* Device model and OS version \r\n* Logs (crash log or logcat)\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*: When switching between Chats, Discover and Contacts then tabs in the bottom of the screen are not updated. For example, Chats can be active but tab highlights Discover tab.\r\n![tab vs screen](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6584810/25566628/1a555aba-2ddd-11e7-9d83-3ac5931ebb3e.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nActive page and active tab in the bottom show the same item. E.g if Discover screen is shown then Discover tab is highlighted.\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\nSometimes tab in the bottom is not updated and wrong element is highlighted. For example, when  Discover screen is shown then Chats tab is highlighted.\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\nVideo (issue but not steps): https://drive.google.com/open?id=0Bz3t9zSg1wb7UC1nSGhmNEpmVFE\r\nNeed help to find exact steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: 0.9.6\r\n* Operating System: Android OS Level 23, Device OnePlus A0001\r\n\r\n### Instabug\r\n* https://dashboard.instabug.com/applications/status-10bb8cbc-15f6-44f0-8c7a-db478dc34d7d/beta/bugs/372",
